snippet.title: The Chronicles of Nyanya
snippet.description:
Trailer for The Chronicles of Nyanya, an RPG about CATS.
Release date is planned for this year.
You can help us by voting here: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=430758391

The movie has been created with the help of Ziemowit Kłujszo: https://www.youtube.com/user/KtoSkopiowal

Thanks for your support!
